[[sn:May 9 (Lunisolar)]] [[ko:음력 5월 9일]] [[ja:5月9日 (旧暦)]] [[zh:五月初九]] [[en:draft:May 9 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:May 9 (lunar calendar)]] [[sn:ay 9 (Lunisolar)]] [[de:9. Mai (Lunisolar)]] [[ar:May 9 (Lunisolar)]]

{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 9''' is the 9th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Genroku|de|Genroku|ja|元禄|zh|元禄|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1691|de|1691|ja|1691|zh|1691|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 5|de|5. Juni|ja|6月5日|zh|6月5日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|de|Tokugawa-Shogunat|ja|徳川幕府|zh|德川幕府|12=draft|12=draft}} granted permission to the wealthy merchant {{ill|Sumitomo family|de|Sumitomo-Familie|ja|住友家|zh|住友家|12=draft|12=draft}} to mine the {{ill|Besshi Copper Mine|de|Besshi-Kupferbergwerk|ja|別子銅山|zh|别子铜山|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Bunkyū|de|Bunkyū|ja|文久|zh|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1862|de|1862|ja|1862|zh|1862|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 6|de|6. Juni|ja|6月6日|zh|6月6日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate's envoy to Europe, {{ill|Takeuchi Hoto|de|Takeuchi Hoto|ja|竹内保徳|zh|竹内保徳|12=draft|12=draft}}, signed the {{ill|London Memorandum|de|London-Memorandum|ja|ロンドン覚書|zh|伦敦备忘录|12=draft|12=draft}} with British Foreign Secretary Russell, and agreed to open the markets of {{ill|Edo|de|Edo|ja|江戸|zh|江户|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Osaka|de|Osaka|ja|大阪|zh|大阪|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Meiji era|de|Meiji-Ära|ja|明治時代|zh|明治时代|lt=Meiji|lt_ja=明治|lt_de=Meiji|lt_zh=Meiji|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|de|1871|ja|1871|zh|1871|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 26|de|26. Juni|ja|6月26日|zh|6月26日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokyo Prefecture|de|Tokio-Präfektur|ja|東京府|zh|东京府|12=draft|12=draft}} announced the establishment of a road classification with a central carriageway and pedestrian sidewalks on both sides.
== Births == * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1867|de|1867|ja|1867|zh|1867|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 11|de|11. Juni|ja|6月11日|zh|6月11日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ino Yoshinori|de|Ino Yoshinori|ja|伊能嘉矩|zh|伊能嘉矩|12=draft|12=draft}}, an anthropologist and folklorist (died {{ill|1925|de|1925|ja|1925|zh|1925|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Meiji era|de|Meiji-Ära|ja|明治時代|zh|明治时代|lt=Meiji|lt_ja=明治|lt_de=Meiji|lt_zh=Meiji|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1870|de|1870|ja|1870|zh|1870|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 7|de|7. Juni|ja|6月7日|zh|6月7日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ishikage Masaomi|de|Ishikage Masaomi|ja|石光真臣|zh|石光真臣|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Military Personnel|de|Militärpersonal|ja|軍人|zh|军人|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1937|de|1937|ja|1937|zh|1937|12=draft|12=draft}}).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kannin|de|Kannin|ja|寛仁|zh|寛仁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julianischer Kalender|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|儒略历|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1017|de|1017|ja|1017|zh|1017|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 5|de|5. Juni|ja|6月5日|zh|6月5日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Sanjō|de|Kaiser Sanjō|ja|三条天皇|zh|三条天皇|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 67th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|de|Kaiser von Japan|ja|天皇|zh|天皇|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|976|de|976|ja|976|zh|976|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Shōkyō|de|Shōkyō|ja|正暦|zh|Shōkyō|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|de|Genkō|ja|元弘|zh|元弘|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julianischer Kalender|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|儒略历|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1333|de|1333|ja|1333|zh|1333|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 21|de|21. Juni|ja|6月21日|zh|6月21日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Chūji|de|Hōjō Chūji|ja|北条仲時|zh|北条仲時|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Busho (Rank)|de|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|zh|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Kamakura shogunate|de|Kamakura-Shogunat|ja|鎌倉幕府|zh|镰仓幕府|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Rokuhara Tandai|de|Rokuhara Tandai|ja|六波羅探題|zh|六波罗探题|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1306|de|1306|ja|1306|zh|1306|12=draft|12=draft}}).
