== Deaths == * {{ill|Kannin|de|Kannin|ja|寛仁|zh|寛仁}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julianischer Kalender|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|儒略历}} {{ill|1017|de|1017|ja|1017|zh|1017}} {{ill|June 5|de|5. Juni|ja|6月5日|zh|6月5日}}) – {{ill|Emperor Sanjō|de|Kaiser Sanjō|ja|三条天皇|zh|三条天皇}}, the 67th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|de|Kaiser von Japan|ja|天皇|zh|天皇}} (died {{ill|976|de|976|ja|976|zh|976}}). * {{ill|Shōkyō|de|Shōkyō|ja|正暦|zh|Shōkyō}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|de|Genkō|ja|元弘|zh|元弘}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julianischer Kalender|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|儒略历}} {{ill|1333|de|1333|ja|1333|zh|1333}} {{ill|June 21|de|21. Juni|ja|6月21日|zh|6月21日}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Chūji|de|Hōjō Chūji|ja|北条仲時|zh|北条仲時}}, {{ill|Busho (Rank)|de|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|zh|武将}} ・{{ill|Kamakura shogunate|de|Kamakura-Shogunat|ja|鎌倉幕府|zh|镰仓幕府}} {{ill|Rokuhara Tandai|de|Rokuhara Tandai|ja|六波羅探題|zh|六波罗探题}} (died {{ill|1306|de|1306|ja|1306|zh|1306}}).
