'''May 9''' is the 9th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Genroku|de|Genroku|ja|元禄|zh|元禄|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1691|de|1691|ja|1691|zh|1691|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 5|de|5. Juni|ja|6月5日|zh|6月5日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|de|Tokugawa-Shogunat|ja|徳川幕府|zh|德川幕府|qq=|12=draft}} granted permission to the wealthy merchant {{ill|Sumitomo family|de|Sumitomo-Familie|ja|住友家|zh|住友家|qq=|12=draft}} to mine the {{ill|Besshi Copper Mine|de|Besshi-Kupferbergwerk|ja|別子銅山|zh|别子铜山|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Bunkyū|de|Bunkyū|ja|文久|zh|文久|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1862|de|1862|ja|1862|zh|1862|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 6|de|6. Juni|ja|6月6日|zh|6月6日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate's envoy to Europe, {{ill|Takeuchi Hoto|de|Takeuchi Hoto|ja|竹内保徳|zh|竹内保徳|qq=|12=draft}}, signed the {{ill|London Memorandum|de|London-Memorandum|ja|ロンドン覚書|zh|伦敦备忘录|qq=|12=draft}} with British Foreign Secretary Russell, and agreed to open the markets of {{ill|Edo|de|Edo|ja|江戸|zh|江户|qq=|12=draft}} and {{ill|Osaka|de|Osaka|ja|大阪|zh|大阪|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Meiji era|de|Meiji-Ära|ja|明治時代|zh|明治时代|lt=Meiji|lt_ja=明治|lt_de=Meiji|lt_zh=Meiji|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorianischer Kalender|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|公历|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|de|1871|ja|1871|zh|1871|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 26|de|26. Juni|ja|6月26日|zh|6月26日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokyo Prefecture|de|Tokio-Präfektur|ja|東京府|zh|东京府|qq=|12=draft}} announced the establishment of a road classification with a central carriageway and pedestrian sidewalks on both sides.

